Kelvin Tay, chief investment 
strategist at UBS Wealth Management in  Singapore , discusses 
Asian stocks and his investment strategy.  Tay also talks about  Europe 's debt crisis, its impact on 
 Asia , and  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  He speaks in Singapore with Susan Li on 
Bloomberg Television's "First Up." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 03:40
 